---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout>
  <article>
    <div>
      Hello! My name is Sylvie&mdash;I use she/they pronouns. I studied physics
      and math in school and now work as a software developer. But I also have
      major interests in fiction, video games, art, and so much more! Truth be
      told, it's kind of hard to put all of that into a single category, so this
      website sort of serves as a grab bag for all of my interests. If you have
      any questions, feel free to reach out to me!
      <a
        class="social-link"
        title="Find me on Github"
        href="https://www.github.com/oneirocosm"
        ><img
          class="logo"
          width="32px"
          height="32px"
          alt="Git Lab website logo"
          src="/src/assets/github-mark.svg"
        /><div>My GitHub</div></a
      >
      <a
        class="social-link"
        title="Find me on Bluesky at oneirocosm"
        href="https://bsky.app/profile/oneirocosm.bsky.social"
        ><img
          class="logo"
          width="28px"
          height="28px"
          alt="Bluesky website logo"
          src="/src/assets/bluesky-color.svg"
        /><div>My Bluesky</div></a
      >
      <a
        class="social-link"
        title="Email me"
        href="mailto:contact@oneirocosm.com"
        ><img
          class="logo"
          width="32px"
          height="32px"
          alt="Email logo"
          src="/src/assets/mail.svg"
        /><div>contact@oneirocosm.com</div></a
      >
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
<style lang="scss">
  .social-link {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 5px;

    .logo {
      object-fit: contain;
    }
  }
</style>
